metatags.title: Bad Salad
metatags.og:title: Bad Salad
metatags.og:description:
Started in 2007 unpretentiously by 3 friends in a small rehearsal room, Bad Salad soon developed into one of Brazil's greatest names of the genre, reaching and enticing fans throughout the world with a groovy mix of technicality, melody and balls.
 
Bad Salad released their debut album "Uncivilized" on July 2012, and the follow up EP "Puzzled" on October 2013, both to great critical acclaim.
